# OWP project files — exclude bloat that can't go to GitHub
# (zips, jobsite videos, photo dumps, large architectural plan sets).
# Keeps Job Detail Reports, contracts, invoices, xlsx summaries, and cortex outputs.
owp/**/*.zip
owp/**/*.mov
owp/**/*.MOV
owp/**/Photos/
owp/**/Plans/

